OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FEx-US bank head to review  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FBank of England forecasts  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Ben Bernanke, the former head of the US
OL,6, central bank, is to lead a review of   
OL,7, the Bank of England's forecasting.     
OL,9,FThe appointment comes as the Bank faces
OL,10,Fcriticism for its efforts to control   
OL,11,Fsoaring prices and failure to predict  
OL,12,Ftheir surge.                           
OL,14,FInflation in the UK was 7.9% last month
OL,15,F- far higher than the 6% peak once     
OL,16,Fforecast by the bank.                  
OL,18,FBank Governor Andrew Bailey said the   
OL,19,Freview would allow the institution to  
OL,20,F"step back and reflect".               
